article.description: James Suber recorded 13 points and 13 rebounds to lead Cal State Bakersfield to a 75-62 win over Chicago State on Thursday night.
article.headline: Suber leads CS Bakersfield over Chicago St. 75-62
article.linkText: Suber leads CS Bakersfield over Chicago St. 75-62
article.story:
CHICAGO --  The Chicago State men's basketball game against Cal State-Bakersfield scheduled for Saturday at 12:05 pm has been moved to Sunday (Jan. 19) at 12:05 p.m. (CST) because of inclement weather in the Chicago area.

Go to GoCSUCougars.com for further information regarding weather updates and changes to the schedule.
